    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Extinct order of extinct flying reptiles of the Mesozoic order characterized by having a fourth digit of each forelimb prolonged to a great length to support a wing membrane for active flight.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
